flowchart LR
    Prev([Controller / Finance Manager]) -- oversees --> Role([Bookkeeper])
    Role --> F1[Record Rent Transactions]
    Role --> F2[Reconcile Bank Accounts]
    Role --> F3[Maintain Split Trust Ledger]
    Role --> F4[Process Vendor Invoices]
    Role --> F5[Prepare Owner Statements]
    Role -- prepares statements for --> Next([Owner / Investor])
    Audit([Auditor]) -. reviews .-> Role
    Compliance([Compliance Officer]) -. audits .-> Role
